851
00:52:01.868 --> 00:52:05.205
You have been lying to me.

852
00:52:05.288 --> 00:52:07.123
you fucking liar!

853
00:52:07.207 --> 00:52:10.126
Skye! Skye! Shit.

854
00:52:10.544 --> 00:52:11.837
Skye!

855
00:52:12.921 --> 00:52:14.047
Skye.

